title: IMFACT tease with a preview image of their upcoming 'IMFACTORY Part 2' release | allkpop.com
text: Or Login / Register With Us Forgot Password? Remember Me IMFACT tease with a preview image of their upcoming 'IMFACTORY Part 2' release By beansss 3 minutes ago 275 0 1 0 Google+ IMFACT is gearing up for the release of their ongoing ' IMFACTORY Part 2 ' project, with a preview image! The image gives fans a sneak preview of the lyrics from the upcoming song, " Please Be My First Love ". Contrary to the title of the song, the revealed lyrics state that " [You] may not be my first love, but [you'll] be my everlasting love" , raising curiosity about the rest of the lyrics' contents. You can listen to "Please Be My First Love" this February 27!
